## 2026-04-03 - handleMultiModeInlineSave and handleDetachFromGenerator missing error handling
- Added try-catch to `handleMultiModeInlineSave` around the PATCH apiFetch call; on failure calls `onError?.()` and returns early, preventing onPushUndo/onRefresh from running after a failed save.
- Added try-catch to `handleDetachFromGenerator` around the PATCH apiFetch call; on failure calls `onError?.()` and returns early. The existing try-catch around the GET fetch was updated to use `onError?.(...)` instead of `console.warn` to match the pattern.
- Added `onError` to the dependency arrays of both callbacks.

